WEBVTT

00:00:07.990 --> 00:00:10.191
Mastering any physical skill,

00:00:10.191 --> 00:00:12.001
be it performing a pirouette,

00:00:12.001 --> 00:00:13.080
playing an instrument,

00:00:13.080 --> 00:00:14.671
or throwing a baseball,

00:00:14.671 --> 00:00:16.100
takes practice.

00:00:16.100 --> 00:00:20.371
Practice is the repetition of an action
with the goal of improvement,

00:00:20.371 --> 00:00:24.580
and it helps us perform with more ease,
speed, and confidence.

